on/china-opinion/article/3260241/who-can-us-really-count-war-china-over-taiwan?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>如果台湾爆发战争，华盛顿可以依靠其盟友，这是最好的情况 — — 更有可能的是，这是一厢情愿的想法。对于华盛顿来说，最大的战略模糊性是，一个强大的中国是否会对和平统一变得更有信心，还是会更加不耐烦并诉诸武力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 21:30:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3260241/who-can-us-really-count-war-china-over-taiwan?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国南方城市广州遭受洪水袭击，龙卷风造成5人死亡</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3260650/tornado-hits-chinas-hail-battered-southern-city-guangzhou-province-battles-deadly-floods-more-rain?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>当局称，周六下午 3 点左右，三级风暴袭来，造成 33 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 14:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3260650/tornado-hits-chinas-hail-battered-southern-city-guangzhou-province-battles-deadly-floods-more-rain?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中法同意在南海紧张局势升级之际深化军事合作</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260645/china-france-agree-deepen-military-cooperation-south-china-sea-tensions-rise?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>法国与美国和菲律宾在有争议的南海水域举行演习之际，与解放军就战区间合作和对话机制达成协议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 13:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260645/china-france-agree-deepen-military-cooperation-south-china-sea-tensions-rise?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国人工智能创新识别食道癌病变的速度是医生肉眼评估的两倍：论文</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3260496/chinese-ai-innovation-identifies-oesophageal-cancer-lesions-double-rate-doctors-assessment-eye-paper?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在内窥镜检查过程中为医生突出显示食道病变的算法现已在中国数百家医院使用。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 12:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3260496/chinese-ai-innovation-identifies-oesophageal-cancer-lesions-double-rate-doctors-assessment-eye-paper?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国一年多前就告别了“零新冠”规则，但北京是否仍然坚持过去？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3260578/china-said-goodbye-zero-covid-rules-over-year-ago-beijing-still-hanging-past?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>新华社呼吁结束“过时的做法”，因为人们对北京仍在实行的一些大流行时期的行动管制（例如地铁出行、医院和校园探访）感到不满。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 11:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3260578/china-said-goodbye-zero-covid-rules-over-year-ago-beijing-still-hanging-past?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“头衔驱动”的研究方法扼杀了中国科技进步的动力</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260519/chinas-drive-tech-progress-stifled-title-driven-research-approach?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国需要更多更好的研究来发掘未来的技术，但基于头衔和参与某些项目的研究文化正在限制其科学家的潜力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 10:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260519/chinas-drive-tech-progress-stifled-title-driven-research-approach?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国批准了95款新游戏，其中包括索尼的《失落的灵魂》和网易的《破碎的土地》</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3260628/china-approves-95-new-video-games-april-including-lost-soul-aside-sony-and-neteases-broken-land?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这是国家新闻出版总署今年迄今为止批准的最小一批视频游戏。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 09:00:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3260628/china-approves-95-new-video-games-april-including-lost-soul-aside-sony-and-neteases-broken-land?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国将如何回应美国与韩国、日本的海军造船计划？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3260494/how-will-china-respond-us-navys-shipbuilding-push-south-korea-japan?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析人士表示，国内工业产能短缺以及对中国主导地位的担忧是吸引亚洲盟友造船厂的原因。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 08:00:09 GMT</pubD